title: The Trendmmy Nods Are In 7/12: JWST, Costco, Heinz, Emmy's, Prefunk

description:
In this edition of The Trendmmy Nods Are In, Jack and super producer Becca discuss the JWST's first images, the Costco hotdog controversy, Heinz Field getting renamed, the 2022 Emmy Nom-Noms, and 'Pregame vs. Prefunk'?
